Pericles</link> in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../420/72420.xml">
429 BC</link>, a new class emerged: that of the wealthy owners and managers of workshops. Examples include <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../338/231338.xml">
Cleon</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../062/419062.xml">
